where identity and access management must span the entirety of AWS.
其中身份和访问管理必须跨越 AWS 的全部 

00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:16.865
Another example is Cloudfront,
另一个示例是 Cloudfront 

00:02:16.865 --> 00:02:21.020
