每个区域都在 AWS 控制台中显示一次 

00:02:28.190 --> 00:02:32.285
but an S3 bucket still lives in a single region.
但 S3 桶仍然生活在一个区域

00:02:32.285 --> 00:02:34.760
One reason for this is that there is
原因之一是

