You must determine if your use case warrants the cost and complexity.
您必须确定您的用例是否需要成本和复杂性 

00:02:42.730 --> 00:02:45.165
As AWS build services,
作为 AWS 构建服务 

00:02:45.165 --> 00:02:48.140
they generally released them at first to only some
他们一般都是先放了一些

